flowchart LR
    CHANGE[Change Request]

    CHANGE --> RFC[RFC / ticket created]
    RFC --> REVIEW{review required?}
    REVIEW -->|low risk| ASYNC[async approval via PR]
    REVIEW -->|high risk| SYNC[sync review: arch + security]
    ASYNC & SYNC --> APPROVE{approved?}
    APPROVE -->|no| REVISE[revise proposal]
    REVISE --> REVIEW
    APPROVE -->|yes| SCHED[schedule deploy window]
    SCHED --> DEPLOY[deploy]
    DEPLOY --> VERIF[post-deploy verification]
    VERIF -->|ok| CLOSE[close ticket]
    VERIF -->|fail| ROLLBACK[rollback + incident]
